  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The UK has officially signed an economic partnership agreement with Japan, marking an historic moment, as the UK’s first major trade deal as an independent trading nation and offering a glimpse of Global Britain’s potential.   </p>

